      • call

        public final AssembliesCreateInstanceResponse call​(String did,
                                                   String wid,
                                                   String eid)
                                            throws OnshapeException
        Calls createInstance method, Create an instance of a part, part studio or assembly into an existing assembly element. If instanceDefinition.isAssembly == true, isWholePartStudio and partId are ignored. If instanceDefinition.isWholePartStudio == true, partId is ignored If both are false, partId must point to a valid part.
        Parameters:
        did - Document ID
        wid - Workspace ID
        eid - Element ID
        Returns:
        Response object
        Throws:
        OnshapeException - On HTTP or serialization error

      • call

        public final AssembliesCreateInstanceResponse call​(OnshapeDocument document)
                                            throws OnshapeException
        Calls createInstance method, Create an instance of a part, part studio or assembly into an existing assembly element. If instanceDefinition.isAssembly == true, isWholePartStudio and partId are ignored. If instanceDefinition.isWholePartStudio == true, partId is ignored If both are false, partId must point to a valid part.
        Parameters:
        document - Document object from Onshape URL.
        Returns:
        Response object
        Throws:
        OnshapeException - On HTTP or serialization error
